Escalation Matrix
Issue Levels:

markdown
Level 1: Basic Support
- Password reset
- Billing questions
- Feature questions
- Handled by: Documentation/Email

Level 2: Technical Support
- Integration issues
- API problems
- Bug reports
- Handled by: Founder (Pierre)

Level 3: Critical Issues
- System downtime
- Data loss
- Security incidents
- Handled by: Founder + Emergency protocol

Level 4: Strategic Support
- Enterprise customization
- Partnership integration
- GDPR compliance questions
- Handled by: Founder + Legal advisor
